    <main>
        <h1>Kyber Crystals of the Force Sensitives</h1>
        <p>Over vast millenniums, where periods of both peace and strife resided together, the force has remained in the background guiding the flow of causality. <br>
        The Jedi battle for peace, prosperity, and order; while their counter parts The Sith wage conflict for their own interests. <br>
        Whether peace or conflict exists, a practitioner of the Force carries an ornate weapon sacred to their order, the Light Saber. <br>
        Below will be a brief introduction to a major component that not only powers their weapon, but signifies how that Force user would like to be recognized.<br> </p>
    </main>
    <!-- The first kyber crystal introduced will be focused on Blue Crystals.  -->

    <section>
        <article class="crystalTypes">
            <h3>Blue Crystals</h3>
            <p>The most common hues found during the Jedi Order.<br> Blue crystals indicated that they were assigned to a Jedi Guardian.<br> </p>

        </article>
    </section>
