    <section>
        <article class="crystalTypes">
            <h3>Purple Crystals</h3>
            <p>A rare color not common within the Jedi Order, Purple Kyber crystals are seldomly seen. The color is associated to members who do not conform with all Order principles.</p>

        </article>
    </section>
    <img src="https://ultrasabers.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/PurpleLightsaber3.jpg" alt="Purple Lightsaber" style="width:250px"/>

    <!--Now on to Sith users and the Red Kyber Crystal.-->
    <section>
        <article class="crystalTypes">
            <h3>Red Crystals</h3>
            <p>Forged and warped through manipulation through the Dark Side of the Force, Red crystal are not of normal origin. The Sith create these twisted crystals to symbolize their anger, hatred, and selfish path they choose to walk.</p>

        </article>
    </section>
